title: Netanyahu says war has entered second phase as troops prepare for ‘long and difficult’ battle
description: Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu warned Saturday of a long and difficult war ahead as troops on the ground say they are prepared for a fight that could last months.

title: Iranian teen Armita Geravand dies weeks after subway incident, state media reports
description: DUBAI, United Arab Emirates — An Iranian teenage girl injured weeks ago in a mysterious incident on Tehran’s Metro while not wearing a headscarf has died, state media reported Saturday.

title: After begging him to return to Thailand, one worker’s family fears he is among Hamas’ hostages
description: More than half of the estimated 220 hostages in Gaza are foreign nationals, the Israeli government says, including 54 from Thailand.

title: Videos of Hamas attack suggest that jihadism has evolved in chilling new ways
description: The brutality and elation of Hamas militants as they killed Israeli civilians is evident in an Israeli government compilation of videos shown to about two dozen journalists in New York on Friday.
